data.description: There is room to breathe in this adorable 3 bedroom 1.5 bath home in Rutherford county! You'll feel like you're in your own nature park with 2 acres of cleared land surrounding the home and an additional 2 acres of woods as a privacy buffer. Unrestricted and with PLENTY of room for gardening, animals, and entertaining space. 18 minutes to the towns of Rutherfordton and Lake Lure, 40 minutes to Hendersonville, and 17 minutes to the Tryon International Equestrian Center. This adorable home is just waiting for you to come and make it your own!
